        <a class="btn btn-small" href="/29113?expandall=true&">Expand Descriptions</a>        <a class="btn btn-small" target="_blank" href="mailto:osg@tick.globalnoc.iu.edu?subject=Open%20Science%20Grid%3A%20Could%20OSG%20CA%20certificates%20be%20used%20for%20email%20signing%3F%20ISSUE%3D29113%20PROJ%3D71"><i class="icon-envelope"></i> Update w/Email</a>
